title: BRIEF-Moody's Says Revised Trans-Pacific Partnership Benefits All Members, But Less Without The U.S.‍​
text:
March 8 (Reuters) -
* MOODY’S - REVISED TRANS-PACIFIC PARTNERSHIP BENEFITS ALL MEMBERS, BUT LESS WITHOUT THE U.S.‍​
